{"TopicId":131230,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Saved games","CreatedByName":"Perotis","CreatedById":155860,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T07:52:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Perotis","CreatedById":155860,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T07:52:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a reason that there isn\u0027t a standard saved game system? \u00A0It would be so much nicer on those long missions where you realize you should have done something different, but you can\u0027t revert your flight. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Baconation","CreatedById":122914,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T07:55:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthere actually is a pretty solid way for saving games like that. just press the ESC button when you\u0027re at the KSC overview and go to save game. you can name it whatever you\u0027d like, and load any of them. you can manually load quicksaves there too. it is essentially where your quicksaves go when you press f5\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FancyMouse","CreatedById":142946,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T08:23:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalt-f5/f9\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bonyetty","CreatedById":57769,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T08:29:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n^ this will let you create, name and load as many saves as you want.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MoonMan22","CreatedById":78400,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-02T13:10:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222390131\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022131230\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221454401389\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142946\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FancyMouse\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, FancyMouse said:\n\u003C/di